Package: geosam
Title: Geospatial Image Segmentation with SAM3
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-12-19
Authors@R:
    person("Kyle", "Walker", , "kyle@walker-data.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Native R API for geospatial image segmentation using Meta's
    Segment Anything Model 3 (SAM3). Provides tidyverse-friendly interfaces
    for detecting objects in satellite imagery using text prompts, point prompts,
    and exemplar-based detection. Features open-vocabulary object
    detection powered by SAM3's text prompting. Built-in support for downloading
    satellite imagery from Mapbox, Esri, and MapTiler.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/walkerke/geosam
